VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT context\.lookup\s*\(|jndiContext\.lookup\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:request|getParameter|getHeader|input|\+ && MISSING:allowlist|whitelist|validateJndiName
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects JNDI lookup calls that may resolve attacker-controlled names (Log4Shell-class pattern).
TRACE Externalized rule logic for JNDI Injection: InitialContext Lookup with User Input.
